784
01:14:04.833 --> 01:14:05.833
Constantly.

785
01:14:10.750 --> 01:14:12.333
He called me "Pushi."

786
01:14:15.416 --> 01:14:16.750
He knew I hated that nickname.

787
01:14:20.583 --> 01:14:22.375
I hated it when he treated me like a kid.

788
01:14:23.166 --> 01:14:25.083
But that's what I was. a fucking kid.

789
01:14:29.166 --> 01:14:32.958
That day. I got fed up and I punched
him in the shoulder to make him stop.

790
01:14:36.166 --> 01:14:38.416
That's all I wanted. for him to stop.

791
01:14:40.250 --> 01:14:44.291
So he turned. really pissed off.
and took his eyes off the road.

792
01:14:45.375 --> 01:14:48.833
Suddenly. his window lit up
and the car started skidding.

793
01:14:50.708 --> 01:14:56.083
I covered my face.
and the windshield slashed my wrist.

794
01:14:59.916 --> 01:15:02.500
From one moment to the next.
my brother was gone.

795
