1025
01:45:14.708 --> 01:45:15.791
It's okay. sweetie.

1026
01:45:19.250 --> 01:45:25.458
<i>Even if it hurts. and it won't be easy.</i>
<i>I'm gonna get better. for me and for you.</i>

1027
01:45:27.500 --> 01:45:30.541
<i>Before I met you.</i>
<i>it felt like everything was against me.</i>

1028
01:45:30.625 --> 01:45:32.333
<i>like the world had defeated me.</i>

1029
01:45:33.375 --> 01:45:35.291
<i>And then you showed up.</i>

1030
01:45:38.375 --> 01:45:40.375
<i>Remember the first time we saw each other?</i>

1031
01:45:41.041 --> 01:45:43.208
<i>We ran into each other</i>
<i>at the school entrance.</i>

1032
01:45:43.291 --> 01:45:44.833
LUKE HOWLAND
06-15-2006 - 12-05-2025

1033
01:45:44.916 --> 01:45:47.166
<i>I looked into your eyes</i>
<i>and gave you my heart.</i>

1034
