ALWAYS IN OUR HEARTS.
YOUR LIGHT LIVES ON IN US.

1035
01:45:51.791 --> 01:45:54.208
<i>Remember the first time we kissed?</i>

1036
01:45:54.291 --> 01:45:58.291
<i>I wanted to die. That night.</i>
<i>I was the happiest person in the world.</i>

1037
