1038
01:46:03.750 --> 01:46:06.833
<i>I was about to fall.</i>
<i>but you didn't let go of my hand.</i>

1039
01:46:19.166 --> 01:46:22.458
<i>I love you and I always will</i>
<i>until you stop remembering me.</i>

1040
01:46:23.208 --> 01:46:27.166
<i>Until I turn to dust</i>
<i>and my soul ceases to exist.</i>

1041
01:46:30.416 --> 01:46:33.291
<i>Because my dream will only be fulfilled</i>
<i>if you are in it.</i>

1042
01:46:44.916 --> 01:46:47.500
<i>So I'm asking you</i>
<i>to take care of yourself while I'm away.</i>

1043
01:46:47.583 --> 01:46:49.416
<i>Because if you call me crying one night.</i>

1044
01:46:49.500 --> 01:46:52.541
<i>I swear I'll go crazy</i>
<i>and take the first flight to come hug you.</i>

1045
01:46:53.458 --> 01:46:55.750
<i>I know you can do it. You're strong.</i>

1046
01:46:56.875 --> 01:46:59.625
<i>And please take care of the boulevard</i>
<i>in my absence. okay?</i>

1047
01:47:01.000 --> 01:47:04.791
<i>I love you. Hasley Weigel. No matter</i>
<i>the distance or the time that separate us.</i>

1048
01:47:04.875 --> 01:47:07.666
<i>I will always love you.</i>
<i>In this life and a thousand more.</i>

1049
